/*
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/CITATION.cff
!/requirements.txt
!/paper_revC/
!/src/
!/configs/
!/scripts/
!/baselines/
!/outputs/
!/results/
!/madifft_final/
!/privacy_attacks/
!/data/

# Explicitly excluded (also covered by root /* deny but listed for clarity):
#   Sal_smart/, physics_ab/, rag_intervention_audit/
#   data_exports/, tmp_*/, notebooks/, "relevant papers/", "New folder*/"
#   experiments/, paper_outputs/, generated_tables/, release_bundle/
#   outputs_ml/, dp_runs.json, FINAL_WORK_SUMMARY.md, etc.

# Global junk / environments / caches
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
**/.ipynb_checkpoints/
**/*.tmp
**/*.temp
**/*.bak
**/*.orig
**/*.rej
**/*.zip
**/*.log
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
.venv/
venv/
env/

# Keep all paper_revC source, but only the approved compact results
paper_revC/external/
paper_revC/results_revC/*
!paper_revC/results_revC/POP6_SEEDED_20260321/
!paper_revC/results_revC/DOMIAS_POP6_SEEDED_20260321/
